{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/Tyke_and_co_torn_shadow__1_.png?t=1729775393\" /><br>Welcome to Pine Hearts Caravan Park! As Tyke, hop into your hiking boots and explore the paths and rivers of this cosy little world. Rummage around the park and find handy tools that will help you on your journey as you fill out your trusty hillwalking journal. Rediscover memories of Tyke's time in the park many summers ago and unearth the heartfelt story of his childhood.<br><br>\ud83d\udc69\u200d\ud83c\udf3e Make new friends<br>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Unlock tools and abilities<br>\ud83c\udfd5\ufe0f Rediscover memories<br>\ud83d\udc36 Pet cute dogs<br>Every inch of the park has little surprises waiting for you to discover!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/NPCs_torn_shadow__1_.png?t=1729775393\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/BridgeWalk__600x360_.gif?t=1729775393\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/Tyke_and_Dad_torn_shadow__1_.png?t=1729775393\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">A Touching Tale</h2>Pine Hearts is a warm, thoughtful game about love, life, memories, and family. It tells a story of the loss of a family member with tenderness and care, but please be aware of this subject matter before playing the game \u2764\ufe0f<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/Memory_2.gif?t=1729775393\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/Critters_torn_shadow__1_.png?t=1729775393\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Wholesome Classics</h2>Pine Hearts takes the item-based progression of Zelda, combines it with Souls-like level design and wraps it all up in a wholesome aesthetic with a focus on puzzles, not combat \ud83c\udf33<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/GargoylePuzzle__600x360_.gif?t=1729775393\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/Tyke_and_Dad_memeory_pals_torn_shadow__1_.png?t=1729775393\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">No Barriers To Play</h2>We\u2019ve worked hard to make Pine Hearts as accessible as possible. Some of the key Accessibility features include:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Simplified Controls<br></li><li>Colour Blocking Mode <br></li><li>Black and White Mode<br></li><li>High Contrast Mode<br></li><li>Visual FX Toggles<br></li><li>Font Scaling<br></li><li>Full Controller/KB+M Remapping</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1781010/extras/ColourBlock__600x360_.gif?t=1729775393\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Pine Hearts Run Free","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/e2b23fa5284f5ac1b9340e9f7a274bbbe7af30e0.jpg"},{"name":"Gruffumpkin Mystery","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/fadaf31249266be9b4a5f43fde45582f8e3ffc72.jpg"},{"name":"Granny's Gala","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/f7f89e4167df45a0515de0329b0ea0460b68bc0c.jpg"},{"name":"Par for the Course","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/ba322eac87dc9c52d266af1958c586d7b182db93.jpg"},{"name":"Not Ready Yet...","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/1401a2fc652a01dedc8cec479f47fdb0995ae075.jpg"},{"name":"Bon Voyage","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1781010/418c1432d7afad45b4478ab4571897f8820d054b.jpg"},{"name":"Lost